DynaMiFLiC v1.0
Copyryght (c) 2012 - slacknux <slacknux@gmail.com>
http://www.slacknux.net


DynaMiFLiC (Dynamic, Minimal, Fast, Light, Cool) is a blogging CMS written in python (>=2.6) with a command line client and a text files database.


===Installation===
1. Launch client.py in the client directory and fill out all required fields
2. Config and config.py files will be created in the client and server/cgi-bin directories.
3. Upload the whole server directory's content on your server


=====Features=====
1. Create new articles
2. Edit articles
3. Edit comments
4. Remove articles
5. Remove comments
6. Download the database
7. Error log
8. Command history
9. Autocomplete
10. BBCode syntax support
